  "title": "Branch Banking Sales Executives/ MNC/ Paid Training Provided",
  "description": "<p><strong>Local Bank</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Basic From $3600 to $4200 + $300 monthly allowance &amp; Incentives<br>\n• Paid training will be provided<br>\n• Fast track progression in the Banking and Finance industry</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• Work closely with the team to manage clients’ portfolios, perform financial analysis<br>\n• Follow the existing list of clients provided by the company<br>\n• Maintain customer loyalty and promote brand identity by providing excellent customer service through regular updates and reviews with customers on financial services/information<br>\n• Assisting in wealth preservation and capital growth<br>\n• Attend to the walk-in and queuing customers and customize solutions to meet clients’ financial objectives</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>•Degree or Local Diploma in any discipline<br>\n•Good communication skills, strong customer service mindset<br>\n• Keen interests in the Banking and Finance industry<br>\n• Be proactive, a good listener, and people-oriented<br>\n• Willingness to learn as comprehensive training provided</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Attractive Basic Salary Package up to $$4200 Basic + $300 Allowance + Commission + Full Employment Benefits + Fast-track Progressions in Bank!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For Fast Response, please Email your updated resume in MS Word format with the following details to <strong>steven@starrecruitment.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1) Last Drawn Salary<br>\n2) Expected Salary<br>\n3) Recent Photo<br>\n4) Reason(s) for Leaving<br>\n5) Availability Period<br>\n6) References</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Steven Chan<br>\nRegistration No: R1105423<br>\nEA License No: 08C5257</p>",
